Name: Kitten Lost Her Box
About the game: Help tiny Kitten get back her favorite paper box only with her agile actions. In this tight platformer kitten brave hand-crafted challenges, meet cute creatures and finally fight with her old enemy! this 2D platformer made in the style of handled games from the early '90s. Play as Kitten run, jump and stomp to defeat difficult levels. Collect fish to get high score and in the speedrun to get rank around the world.
